      <h3>Our Story</h3>
      <p>
        Nestled in the heart of Joviedsa Island in Washington State, Moffat Bay Lodge was created to offer guests a peaceful and immersive island experience. Approved by the San Juan Islands First Nations Development Committee, this resort is a tribute to the natural beauty and cultural richness of the region.
      </p>
