      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>
        Our mission is to provide a relaxing escape where adventure meets comfort. Whether you’re here for a weekend getaway or an extended stay, we aim to deliver outstanding hospitality rooted in sustainability and respect for the island’s heritage.
      </p>
    </div>
